description: This is just a little skill that tells you how many days until the next Christmas. It can be prompted using the keyword 'Santa Countdown', which makes it fun for all. Be sure to check for the special message on Christmas day!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Santa Countdown how long until Christmas
Alexa, ask Santa Countdown how many days until Christmas
name: Christmas Countdown
shortDescription: A skill that allows you to ask how many days until the next Christmas!
